    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "More precisely, it was a vessel with a remarkably large sail-plan (surface area of sails)—ideal for moving people or cargo as fast as possible.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "Ship builders once made a fortune building and selling the ships for profit, both for the trip between China and England (during the mid-1800 tea-trade), and between New York and San Fransisco (during the",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "California Gold Rush",
          "marks": [
            "link-0"
          ]
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": ").",
          "marks": []
        }
      ],
      "markDefs": [
        {
          "_key": "link-0",
          "_type": "link",
          "href": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Gold_rush#/media/File:California_Clipper_500.jpg"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "It’s a great case-study to say the least. Not the least because the shipwrights who build them were in search of tea or gold. But because, by the craze of greed and",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "groupthink",
          "marks": [
            "link-0"
          ]
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "(and the good sense to avoid them)—",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "these",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "merchants found a better (albiet more modest) way to make it rich.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ],
      "markDefs": [
        {
          "_key": "link-0",
          "_type": "link",
          "href": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bandwagon_effect"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "Not with tea or gold. But with the means to go out and find it.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
